{"data":[{"id":563839426,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563839426","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-da18aa868b88b1240fef9ecd52a5a1f1_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546296799,"updated_time":1546394085,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":10,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"nobody","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"disallowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e忍不住要称赞一句：字写的挺工整的。「证明过程」可以总结如下\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eI.\u003c/b\u003e他首先「证明」了三句不需要任何证明的正确的废话（且不用看那莫名其妙的证明）：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e哥德巴赫猜想成立\u003cb\u003e或者\u003c/b\u003e对于任意正整数 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%3D%28-1%29%2B%282n%2B1%29\" alt=\"2n=(-1)+(2n+1)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ；\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e哥德巴赫猜想成立\u003cb\u003e或者\u003c/b\u003e对于任意正整数 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%3D%28-3%29%2B%282n%2B3%29\" alt=\"2n=(-3)+(2n+3)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ；\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e哥德巴赫猜想成立\u003cb\u003e或者\u003c/b\u003e对于任意正整数 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%3D%28-5%29%2B%282n%2B5%29\" alt=\"2n=(-5)+(2n+5)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ；\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e注：证明原文写的「 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cforall+n%5Cin+%5Cmathbf%7BN%7D_%2B+2n%5Cin+B\" alt=\"\\forall n\\in \\mathbf{N}_+ 2n\\in B\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 」稍作修改便对应于「哥德巴赫猜想成立（任一大于2的\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%25E5%2581%25B6%25E6%2595%25B0\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e偶数\u003c/a\u003e，都可表示成两个\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E6%2595%25B0\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e素数\u003c/a\u003e之和。）」。只需改成「对于任意大于 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2\" alt=\"2\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 的正整数 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%5Cin+B\" alt=\"2n\\in B\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 」。「证明」中所写的所谓「哥德巴赫猜想变式一二三」对应于上面三条命题。虽然是废话，却是逻辑正确的。最高票的那几个答案基本上是在抱怨这三句逻辑正确的废话的证明过程有问题。中科大XXX博士的答案完全就是五十步笑一百步的胡扯：连「逆反命题」这种东西都写出来了；这是有多「逆反」？）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eII.\u003c/b\u003e然后，他用极其混乱的逻辑（\u003cb\u003e这是最要命的一步\u003c/b\u003e：「……不符合偶=质+质，故舍」），\u003cb\u003e否定\u003c/b\u003e了下面三条\u003cb\u003e真命题\u003c/b\u003e：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e对于任意正整数 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%3D%28-1%29%2B%282n%2B1%29\" alt=\"2n=(-1)+(2n+1)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ；\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e对于任意正整数 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%3D%28-3%29%2B%282n%2B3%29\" alt=\"2n=(-3)+(2n+3)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ；\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e对于任意正整数 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%3D%28-5%29%2B%282n%2B5%29\" alt=\"2n=(-5)+(2n+5)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ；\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eIII.\u003c/b\u003e最后他宣布：哥德巴赫猜想成立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（附上本回答的链接：\u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/307595822/answer/563839426\" class=\"internal\"\u003e高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？\u003c/a\u003e）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-fba7e8b6fcadb30dfa4e0d00a44d7156_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1334\" data-rawheight=\"1717\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-fba7e8b6fcadb30dfa4e0d00a44d7156_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1334\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-fba7e8b6fcadb30dfa4e0d00a44d7156_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1334'%20height='1717'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1334\" data-rawheight=\"1717\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-fba7e8b6fcadb30dfa4e0d00a44d7156_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1334\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-fba7e8b6fcadb30dfa4e0d00a44d7156_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-fba7e8b6fcadb30dfa4e0d00a44d7156_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-42b3dd484d93c5904607c576df512858_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1435\" data-rawheight=\"1746\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-42b3dd484d93c5904607c576df512858_b.jpg\" class=\"